('Roundup Ultra MAX', 'Glyphosate', 'Glycine', 'EPSPS inhibitor (9)', 'Soluble Liquid', 'herbicide', 'weed', 'Monsanto', ARRAY['Fallow','Pasture','All crops (pre-plant)','Non-crop'], ARRAY['Annual Ryegrass','Wild Radish','Capeweed','Barnyard Grass','Bindweed','Fleabane','Sowthistle'], '1.5-3.0 L/ha', '0 days', '4 hours', 'Broad-spectrum non-selective. Apply to actively growing weeds. Do not apply to drought-stressed weeds.', 'HRAC Group 9. Widespread glyphosate resistance in Australia — particularly ryegrass and fleabane.', '49321'),

