('Sakura 850 WG', 'Pyroxasulfone', 'Isoxazoline', 'VLCFA inhibitor (K3)', 'Wettable Granule', 'herbicide', 'weed', 'Kumiai', ARRAY['Wheat','Barley','Canola','Chickpea'], ARRAY['Annual Ryegrass','Wild Oat','Brome Grass','Canary Grass','Phalaris'], '0.12-0.18 kg/ha', '0 days (pre-emergent)', '12 hours', 'Pre-emergent application — requires rainfall or irrigation for activation. Excellent ryegrass control.', 'HRAC Group K3. Relatively new — monitor for resistance development.', '78342'),

('Intervix', 'Imazamox + Imazapyr', 'Imidazolinone', 'ALS inhibitor (B)', 'Soluble Concentrate', 'herbicide', 'weed', 'BASF', ARRAY['Clearfield Wheat','Clearfield Canola','Clearfield Barley'], ARRAY['Annual Ryegrass','Wild Radish','Prickly Lettuce','Brome Grass','Wild Oat'], '0.6 L/ha', '60 days', '12 hours', 'Only use in Clearfield varieties. Do not follow with sensitive crops for 12 months.', 'HRAC Group B. Cross-resistance with sulfonylureas widespread. Do not use where B-group resistance detected.', '75234'),

('Amicide 625', 'Amine 625 (2,4-D)', '2,4-D', 'Auxin mimic (O)', 'Soluble Concentrate', 'herbicide', 'weed', 'Nufarm', ARRAY['Wheat','Barley','Oats','Pasture','Non-crop'], ARRAY['Capeweed','Sowthistle','Bindweed','Wild Radish','Clover'], '0.5-2.0 L/ha', '7 days', '24 hours', 'Apply in 3-4 leaf stage of cereal. Avoid drift to sensitive broadleaf crops. Do not use in high temperatures.', 'HRAC Group O. Some resistance documented in wild radish in WA.', '12481'),

